Collections.rule:
Individual: @E*
Types: Registrations
Facts: registrationsCourseInstance @A*,
	registrationsStudents @B*,
	registrationStatus @C*,
	grade @D*

Individual: @F*
Types: ProgramInstance
Facts: piProgramCode @A*,
	piStudyYear @B*(xsd:integer),
	piAcademicYear @C*,
	piCourse @D*,
	piCourseType @E*

Individual: @D*
Types: CourseInstance
Facts: planNumStudents @'Course_plannings'!B* (xsd:integer),
	studyPeriod @B*,
	cAcademicYear @C*,
	seniorHours @'Course_plannings'!C*(xsd:float),
	assistHours @'Course_plannings'!D*(xsd:float),
	instanceID @D*,
	examiner @E*,
	ciCourseCode @A*

Individual: @F*
Types: Students
Facts: studentName @A*,
	startYear @D* (xsd:integer),
	graduated @E* (xsd:boolean),
	sProgram @C*,
	studentID @B*

Individual: @E*
Types: TeachingAssignment
Facts: hoursCourseInstance @A*,
	hoursTeacher @B*,
	rHours @D* (xsd:float),
	aHours @D* (xsd:float)

Individual: @B*
Types: Program
Facts: programName @A*,
	pDepartment @C*,
	director @D*,
	programCode @B*

Individual: @E*
Types: Teacher
Facts: teacherName @A*,
	tDivision @D*,
	tDepartment @C*,
	teacherID @B*

Individual: @E*
Types: SeniorTeacher
Facts: teacherName @A*,
	tDivision @D*,
	tDepartment @C*,
	teacherID @B*

Individual: @B*
Types: Course
Facts: credits @C* (xsd:float),
	courseName @A*,
	courseLevel @D*,
	cProgram @G*,
	cDivision @F*,
	courseCode @B*
